urdu transliteration text:
Boli hongi Ali Akbar ko saja ker ZainabChaand ko mere kissi ki na nazar le jaayePaas Zainab ke bacha kya hai jo ghar lejaaye
When she got Ali Akbar ready, Zainab must have said
@HujjatELC

Sochti hogi yeh Bano mera bach jaaye suhaagHurmula mujh sai mere lakht-e-jiger lejaayePaas Zainab ke bacha kya hai jo ghar lejaaye
Hurmala is taking away my beloved one
@HujjatELC
